Rap battle? Nah. #WrapBattle! We want to see you find your holiday cheer, get into the gift giving mood and wrap away! Feel free to challenge Cardi B and Offset and see how you stack up. Videos with the most shares will win epic prizes.

No purchase necessary. Contest begins 11/30 at 12am PST and ends 12/9 at 11:59pm PST. Open to residents of the US, 18+ years old, or with parent/legal guardian permission. Each share counts as an entry, limit 10. Prizes include: (i) 3 VIP tickets to music festival in Indio, CA; (ii) 1 smartphone; (iii) Disneyland experience for winner and guest; (iv) streetwear gift box; (v) 5 TikTok gift boxes; (vi) Trip to the electronic dance festival in Las Vegas, NV. Total ARV of prizes: $16,897. Void where prohibited. See http://bit.ly/tt-wrapbattle for prize details and official rules.

TikTok has a new REACT feature! 💥 Watch our official video to learn how to use it, and show us the most creative way you can #react. Follow these tips for the best results: 

1. To react, click on the “share” button and find the “react” feature. ⚡️
2. You can only react to videos that are 15 seconds or less. ⏳
3. Use earphones with microphones for the best sound quality.🎤
4. Have fun and be creative! ❤️
